    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-10-27T19:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-10-27T19:00:00-05:00" n="799"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d799">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">867N.01/1215: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Jerusalem</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wadsworth</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="97" xml:id="d799fn97">A similar telegram was sent on the
                        same date to the Minister Resident In Iraq as No. 21.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-10-27T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 27, 1938—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your telegram of October 25, 6 p.m. It is suggested that, in your discretion, you
                    might properly acquaint responsible Arab as well as Jewish inquirers with the
                    Department’s public statement concerning Palestine.<note n="98"
                        xml:id="d799fn98">Press release of October 14, <ref target="#pg_953">p.
                            953</ref>.</note> Should you deem it desirable, you may explain also
                    that the statement represents no change in this Government’s position with
                    respect to that question. (See, in this connection, Department’s Radio Bulletin
                    No. 244.)</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
